summary: Comprehensive export and analysis of all 10 discovered Relume projects for MezTal website. Documents complete extraction status, page counts, structures (hierarchical vs flat), and unique features for each project. Identifies 3 hierarchical projects (MezTal Information Architecture with 40-50 pages, MezTa 8 with 30-35 pages, MezTal 5 with 25-30 pages) and 7 flat projects. Highlights unique content including MezTal 6's operational pages (Trust & Security, Partners, Pricing Model, Templates), MezTal 7's industry coverage (B2B SaaS, FinTech, Real Estate), and MezTal 3's Immersion Trips focus. Provides comparative analysis by structure, page count, unique content, and solutions count. Recommends hybrid approach combining MezTal Information Architecture or MezTa 8 as base with content additions from other projects to achieve 50-60 total pages with complete coverage.
